      <img src="https://d3k81ch9hvuctc.cloudfront.net/company/UQmMRG/images/f92cb9d6-0100-4d14-b938-4fea2499eb06.png" alt="5 Loaves 2 Fish Fundraiser at Dune Bird" class="responsive"/>
      <p>Join us August 12 for the “Big Change Equals Big Change” event in support of 5 Loaves 2 Fish. A beautiful cause, a beautiful evening.</p>
      <p><strong>Note:</strong> We’ll close to the public at 4pm on August 12.</p>
      <div class="button-wrapper">
        <a href="https://mynorthtickets.com/events/4th-annual-big-change-equals-big-change-fundraiser-for-5loaves2fish-8-12-2025" class="button">Get Tickets</a>
      </div>
    </div>

