      <img src="https://d3k81ch9hvuctc.cloudfront.net/company/UQmMRG/images/cbdc100b-4e75-4cd8-a8e9-0e691b5228cb.jpeg" alt="Bye Bye Summer Bash at Dune Bird with The Broom Closet Boys" class="responsive"/>
      <p>August 31, 4–7pm — Don’t miss this sendoff with live music by The Broom Closet Boys. Bring a blanket, your crew, and summer vibes.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>🍇 TC Food & Wine Festival</h2>
      <img src="https://d3k81ch9hvuctc.cloudfront.net/company/UQmMRG/images/0036014d-270f-41da-99b8-f4c0370b71d9.png" alt="Traverse City Food and Wine Festival 2025" class="responsive"/>
