      <h2>🦆 Vineyard Tours with Ducks</h2>
      <img src="https://d3k81ch9hvuctc.cloudfront.net/company/UQmMRG/images/85e4debc-3bfe-4b49-9f90-465be1d3e292.png" alt="Indian runner ducks in the vineyard at Dune Bird" class="responsive"/>
      <p>Take a relaxed stroll through the Dune Bird vineyard estate—accompanied by our charming flock of Indian runner ducks! These feathered helpers are part of our regenerative farming practices, helping us naturally manage weeds and pests.</p>
      <p>Learn about our sustainable approach, then enjoy a curated tasting in the tasting room paired with fresh baked goods and locally selected cheeses.</p>
      <p><strong>Available:</strong><br/>🌱 August 20 · 1:30–3:00pm<br/>☀️ August 22 · 10:30am–12:00pm</p>
      <div class="button-wrapper">
        <a href="https://tickets.traversecityfoodandwine.com/location/dune-bird-winery?ev=108" class="button">Get Tour Tickets</a>
      </div>
